    "description": "Always corrosive. The fired rocket sticks to the first object hit; if it hits nothing it halts mid-air, slowly rises, then spins while firing 2 homing rockets per second in all directions for 7 seconds. When the effect ends the parent rocket explodes. Child rockets gain full Amp Shield bonus. Uses 4 ammo per shot, with larger magazine, lower fire rate and slower reload."
